      • isLocked

        boolean isLocked()
        Is the recording locked. Humax PVR sets a flag to say if a recording should be decrypted when it's copied off the disk. This flag is ignored (or at least, always set to decript) for SD files, but not for HD.
        Returns:
        boolean true if its a high def file, and can't be copied, false otherwise.
